&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Opportunity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Enigma is the most reliable, trusted source of data on businesses in the United States. Built on industry-leading entity resolution and the most comprehensive collection of trusted U.S. government data, Enigma powers KYB, screening and AML compliance, merchant payment risk, and go-to-market account-based data enrichment. Enigma provides ground-truth business identity and financial signal data that financial institutions, data platforms, and AI systems rely on to understand and verify businesses, delivered through APIs and Agents to support mission-critical workflows.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll operate as a strategic partner to C-suite stakeholders, applying structured problem-solving to complex business challenges and translating customer needs into product and go-to-market impact.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own client outcomes end-to-end.&lt;/strong&gt; Lead the full lifecycle of our highest-value accounts, from onboarding through retention and expansion with direct accountability for revenue growth and renewal targets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Serve as a strategic advisor.&lt;/strong&gt; Build trusted relationships with C-suite and senior stakeholders, diagnose their most pressing business challenges, and develop tailored strategies for embedding Enigma data into their workflows and decision-making.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drive expansion and commercial growth.&lt;/strong&gt; Identify upsell and cross-sell opportunities, build business cases, and partner with Sales to close expansion deals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Shape product and GTM strategy.&lt;/strong&gt; Synthesize customer feedback and market signals to influence Enigma&#39;s product roadmap and go-to-market positioning. You&#39;ll have a seat at the table.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead complex engagements.&lt;/strong&gt; Design and execute client strategy plans, lead implementation initiatives, and coordinate cross-functional teams (Product, Engineering, Sales) to deliver results.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who You Are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3–5 years of experience&lt;/strong&gt; at a top-tier consulting firm (MBA or equivalent), investment bank, or high-growth technology company, ideally with client-facing or commercial responsibilities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Structured thinker.&lt;/strong&gt; You break down ambiguous problems, develop actionable strategies, and drive execution with rigor.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Commercially minded.&lt;/strong&gt; You understand how to build and defend revenue, and you&#39;re energized by owning a number.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Executive presence.&lt;/strong&gt; You&#39;re comfortable presenting to C-level audiences and navigating complex organizational dynamics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Analytically strong.&lt;/strong&gt; You&#39;re fluent in data, comfortable with SQL and Python, and experienced using data to build narratives and drive decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What Makes This Role Exciting?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ownership with real stakes.&lt;/strong&gt; You&#39;ll have direct influence on Enigma&#39;s largest revenue relationships and the company&#39;s growth trajectory.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic scope.&lt;/strong&gt; Solve complex problems for industry-leading companies while shaping how Enigma builds and sells its products.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Category-defining product.&lt;/strong&gt; Enigma&#39;s unified business identity graph is transforming how companies prospect, onboard, and manage risk and you&#39;ll be at the center of that.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
