&lt;p&gt;This is an exciting time at Enigma. Our products are creating tremendous value for our clients, and we are seeking to expand their capabilities and reach in the market.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an experienced Senior Software Engineer to join our Applied Technologies team. You will play a central role in architecting, building, and managing critical systems in financial crimes prevention and broader risk mitigation, working with teammates and clients to solve high-impact, real-world problems.&lt;/p&gt;
